.SH NAME
gnutls_audit_push_context \- API function
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B #include <gnutls/gnutls.h>
.sp
.BI "void gnutls_audit_push_context(long " context ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "long context" 12
an opaque context
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Push a new crypto\-auditing context to the thread\-local context
stack. The call must match the following \fBgnutls_audit_pop_context()\fP
call. This is useful for the applications that define their own
probe points for application level protocols.
